<episodedetails><title>Strike on Iran: The Nuclear Question (2026)</title><plot>Amid new attacks by the U.S. and Israel, FRONTLINE continues to investigate Iran's nuclear program. This is an updated and expanded investigation of the December 16, 2025 program, drawing on reporting in Iran and in-depth forensic analysis with The Washington Post, Evident Media and Bellingcat.</plot></episodedetails>